node.text:
M E M O R I E S

What did your little ones weigh when they were born? We had a 6 lber, a 7 lber & an 8 lber. 

With this fabulous memory box you can record all those precious details to share with your little one, as they grow! It’s also a fab place to store keepsakes like those teeny first shoes ♥️

📷 huge thanks to Hector & his mum @fiandherhouse 

#littledutch #littledutch_official #littledutchtoys #memorybox #babykeepsakes #babymemorybox #babykeepsake #newborn #newborngift #keepsakebox #personalisedbabygift #newbornessentials #babyshower #babyshowergift #newbabygift #babygirlgift #babyboygift #itsaboy #itsagirl #reels #life #smile #wip #baby #milestones #babymilestones #giftideas #love #welcometotheworld #cutebabies

node.text:
Sleep like a baby 👶🏼 💤 

What does this saying mean in your house? Snoozing the night away or face kicks at 2, 3 & 4am?? 

Sleep is a hot topic here at Scandibørn HQ, so we’ve teamed up with sleep experts @littledreamsconsultingltd to help dispel some of those common myths! Head to our blog to read about “The Secrets of Sleep” & then pop back here at 7.30pm, for a story take over with the wonderful Jenna ♥️

📷 thanks to the lovely @theaikenhaus
